<L>__{exterior market place (day) medium shot}
<A>__{the camera moves in behind the stabbed arab. the knife is still in his back. we get a glimpse of his hands, vainly groping behind him. the camera moves with him as he staggers out into the open market place. his shadow on the ground shows us the silhouette of the knife handle sticking out from his back. the camera moves in close to follow the agony of his head and shoulders as he attempts to go forward.}
